description._content: Original Collection: Harriet's Collection Item Number: HC0596 Image Description: Corvallis fire department is shown on Madison Street near the Masonic Building and City Hall. Photo is of the only horse team the fire department ever had. You can find this image by searching for the item number by clicking here. Want more? You can find more digital resources online.
